<emphasis box="[384,596,1058,1082]" italics="true" pageId="8" pageNumber="7">Rutela terminata</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation author="Le Peletier de Saint-Fargeau, A. L. M. &amp; J. G. de Audinet-Serville" box="[604,1366,1057,1082]" pageId="8" pageNumber="7" pagination="315 - 317" refId="ref11869" refString="Le Peletier de Saint-Fargeau, A. L. M., and J. G. de Audinet-Serville. 1825. Rtele [sic], Rutela p. 315 - 317. In: P. A. Latreille, A. L. M. Le Peletier de Saint-Fargeau, J. G. Audinet-Serville, and F. E. Guerin-Meville (eds.). Encyclopedie Methodique. Histoire naturelle. Entomologie, ou histoire naturelle des Crustaces, des Arachnides et des Insectes, volume 10, part 2. Agasse; Paris, France. 833 p." type="book chapter" year="1825">Le Peletier de Saint-Fargeau and Audinet-Serville, 1825: 317</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
, valid subsequent designation by 
<bibRefCitation author="Ohaus, F." box="[527,752,1089,1114]" pageId="8" pageNumber="7" refId="ref12804" refString="Ohaus, F. 1934 b. Coleoptera lamellicornia, Fam. Scarabaeidae, Subfam. Rutelinae. T. 1: Tribus Rutelini. Genera Insectorum Fasc. 199 A: 172 p." type="book" year="1934">Ohaus 1934b: 125</bibRefCitation>
.
</paragraph>
